Olpiyayati le mbuku o lkuoo le Ker


1   Nadol sii te nkaina e tatene e ilo otonita to lorika le nkitoo olpiyayati le embuku naigero atua o oriong, netipikaki ilmishiren oopishana. 
2  Nadol sii olmalaika ogol elimu to ltoilo sapuk ajo, “Ai eishiaakino nebol ele piyayati le mbuku nebol lelo mishiren lenyena.” 
3  Nemeetae hoo obo te keper aashu te nkop aashu tiabori enkop oidima atabolo ilo piyayati aashu aing'ura atua. 
4  Naishir oleng amu eitu etumi oltung'ani hoo obo oishiaakino pee edol ilo piyayati arishu eing'or atua. 
5   Naajoki nanu obo le lelo payiani lo losho le Yuda, mintoki aishir. Ng'ura, olng'ur le ntonai e Daudi etimirishe peyie etum atabolo ilo piyayati o lelo mishiren lenyena oopishana. 
6   Ore te rishata o lorika le nkitoo ore ng'uesi ong'uan naaishu, o tiatua ilpayiani, nadol olkuoo le ker eitashe, etiu anaa keteyiang'aki apa, neeta mowuarak naapishana o nkonyek naapishana, naa ninche nkiyang'eta naapishana e Nkai, naairriwayioki meshomo enkop pooki. 
7  Nelo nedumu ilo piyayati le mbuku te nkaina e tatene e ilo otonita to lorika le nkitoo. 
8   Ore ake pee edumu ilo piyayati le mbuku, nebatata nena ng'uesi naaishu ong'uan te dukuya ilo kuoo le ker, nemeetae ake enemeibung'ita enkawuo oo sinkolioitin, o ngirran e sahabu naabore empuruonarropil naa enkomono oo sinyat. 
9   Nerany osinkolio ng'ejuk aajo,

“Kinchiaakino iyie pee idumu olpiyayati le embuku,

nibel ilmishiren lenyena.

Amu kiteyieng'aki apa naa to sarge lino inyiang'aka Enkai

iltung'ana aitung'uaa loshon pooki, o lng'ejepa, o ltung'ana o loreren.


10   Nintaa ninche enkitoria o lapolosak le Enkai ang,

naa keyooki ninche aaitoreisho te nkop.”


11   Naing'orisho nanu naning emanita olorika le nkitoo o nena ng'uesi naaishu o lelo payiani oltoilo loo lmalaika kumok. Ore esiana enye naa iip nkuyu iip nkuyu, iip nkuyu, nkalifuni o nkalifuni. 
12  Nejo ninche to ltoilo sapuk, “Eishiakino ilo Kuoo le ker apa oteyiang'aki, te neng'amu engolon, o enkarsisisho, o eng'eno nagut, o enkidimata, o enkanyit, o enkitoo, o emayianata.” 
13  Naning nena pooki naaiseuseu te keper o te nkop oti abori enkop o naatii enaiposha, o nena pooki naatae ejo, “Metaa ene ilo otonita to lorika le nkitoo neaku eno lkuoo le ker, emayianata o enkanyit o enkisisa o enkidimata intarasi o ntarasi!”


14  Nejo nena ng'uesi ong'uan naaishu, “Esai.” Nebatata ilpayiani aaserem.

